<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Ride Booked</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="message-container">
        <h1>Ride Successfully Booked!</h1>
        <p>
            Your ride from <strong><%= startingPoint %></strong> to 
            <strong><%= destination %></strong> has been successfully booked for 
            a fare of <strong>$<%= fare %></strong>.
